    "offset": 360822,
    "slot_size": 258,
    "data_size": 254,
    "nom_orig": "Eikichi",
    "texte_orig": "Phew...[SP]Then[SP]of[SP]course[SP]I[SP]don't[SP]understand.\nI'm[SP]sure[SP]I[SP]would[SP]have[SP]if[SP]it[SP]had[SP]been[SP]English\nor[SP]French.[SP]What[SP]a[SP]letdown.",
