  {
    "id": 5,
    "offset": 361080,
    "slot_size": 258,
    "data_size": 254,
    "nom_orig": "Eikichi",
    "texte_orig": "Hey,[SP]if[SP]one[SP]ideal[SP]comes[SP]true,[SP]is[SP]that[SP]all[SP]you\nget?[SP]Can't[SP]you[SP]find[SP]a[SP]new[SP]dream[SP]and[SP]start[SP]all\nover[SP]chasing[SP]that[SP]one?",
