  {
    "id": 6,
    "offset": 361338,
    "slot_size": 276,
    "data_size": 272,
    "nom_orig": "Eikichi",
    "texte_orig": "If[SP]you're[SP]constantly[SP]chasing[SP]dreams[SP]and[SP]pursuing\ngoals,[SP]won't[SP]you[SP]avoid[SP]becoming[SP]a[SP]shadowman\neven[SP]if[SP]they[SP]take[SP]your[SP]energy?",
