    "data_size": 290,
    "nom_orig": "Ginko",
    "texte_orig": "Jun...[SP]I[SP]don't[SP]want[SP]to[SP]evolve[SP]by[SP]sacrificing\nso[SP]many[SP]people...\n[E1][E2][E4][NULL][NULL]\"Ginko\nMee-ho[SP]and[SP]Sheba[SP]becoming[SP]shadowmen...\nThat's[SP]not[SP]my[SP]ideal.",
