  {
    "id": 14,
    "offset": 363128,
    "slot_size": 300,
    "data_size": 296,
    "nom_orig": "Maya",
    "texte_orig": "The[SP]people[SP]think[SP]the[SP]terrorist[SP]attacks[SP]are[SP]the\nfault[SP]of[SP]the[SP]Masked[SP]Circle.[SP]So[SP]rumors[SP]spread\nthat[SP]they're[SP]an[SP]evil[SP]cult,[SP]and[SP]they[SP]came[SP]true.",
