  {
    "id": 17,
    "offset": 363754,
    "slot_size": 292,
    "data_size": 288,
    "nom_orig": "Maya",
    "texte_orig": "People[SP]now[SP]don't[SP]have[SP]the[SP]courage[SP]to[SP]hold[SP]an\nideal.[SP]A[SP]single[SP]dream[SP]of[SP]theirs[SP]comes[SP]true[SP]and\nthey[SP]forget[SP]what[SP]it[SP]was[SP]like[SP]to[SP]pursue[SP]it.",
